Class SimpleRow

  • java.lang.Object
    • stanford.androidlib.data.SimpleCursor
      • stanford.androidlib.data.SimpleRow
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cursor, Closeable, AutoCloseable, Iterable<SimpleRow>

    public class SimpleRow
extends SimpleCursor
    A SimpleRow object represents one row of a SQLite database query result. See the SimpleCursor class for detailed documentation. 
         for (SimpleRow row : SimpleDatabase.rows(myCursor)) { ... }
